Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:02.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在耀眼的清風之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:05.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}繪畫你的笑顏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:11.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能坦白面對的瞬間
