Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================TEXT================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這個來電鈴聲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你好 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi~ 我是大家的偶像 筱之之束哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要掛斷啊小箒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀啊呀啊呀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾妹喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來電的目的我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於你的專用機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然已經準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高到犯規的性能喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}(High End)　(Over Spec)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟「小白」平起平坐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台機體的名字叫...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「紅椿」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:18.59,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,1000)\pos(937,270)}Oceans·Eleven\N 到了海邊已經十一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經早上了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候鑽進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋快遮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知夫婦就該坦誠相見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更別說你還是我的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這陣子都在說什麼胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本不是都稱喜歡的對象為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺老婆或是我的老婆麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰給你灌輸這些錯誤的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還必須多做些寢技的練習喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要磨練寢技的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是不可以當你的練習對象喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這個時候要臉紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上的練習要開始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}那是什麼啊真是太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放鬆自己是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無禮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然擅自闖入夫婦的寢室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫婦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下箒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天誅~！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早起來就如此杯具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那個啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼今天只邀請了我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要去臨海學校了不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前不是說過沒有女式泳衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我自己也要買
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就順便把你拉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了反正我想也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說好兩人獨處的時候就這麼叫的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記起來了不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄少女純情的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被馬踢死算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得那樣的傢伙死了最好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽手的話就原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不熟悉的街道迷路可就麻煩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好抓緊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是不是手牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是牽著喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既沒有看錯也不是在做白日夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好那殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞拉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必如此警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下我並未打算對你們不利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是加入他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面面對未知的敵人之時先進行情報收集才是道理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下要做的就是追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄清楚兩個人的關係究竟到何程度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點道理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶夏洛特我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正大家都知道你是女生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特這個稱呼會不會太過普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想有沒有別的稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在我們倆之間使用的稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得夏露怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又順口又親切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來很中意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些特別的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以先走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要買點其他東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿好了喔老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下來的後果你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說這買的也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初三的夏天可是特別的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳池用泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海濱用泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決勝泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級決勝泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超超級決勝泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣的都要準備好防止意外情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼意外情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是來買東西的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們買了這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是游泳用具麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊這傢伙鼓足乾勁說要穿給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不必掛心話說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏也是來買泳衣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上要去臨海學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道的話就讓一夏來選了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明年就是一夏的後輩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說選了IS學園…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對是第一志願
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入學考試要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了老哥呢到底哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏來這邊下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿老哥沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬把我拉到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選的泳衣合不合適
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓你幫我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不必一起進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是發現了我們的跟踪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}今年推薦的都是襯托胸部的泳衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是泳衣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上原來有如此多種類的泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好選選不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿不適合的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定一下子就被男朋友討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算其他地方都是滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳裝不好看也是致命的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了的話絕對會來搗亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有誰麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰誰都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問那麼多了你就呆在這裡很快就換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想太多弄成這樣了接下來該怎麼辦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真真的脫了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好不能去想像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想別的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個圓周率是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,π 等於
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.1415926535897932384626499832
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為非常合適
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這件了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織織織斑同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德諾阿同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要知道男??女有別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女兩人都進入試衣間是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到老師也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子出去會很不妙的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微觀察下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉麗莎是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞拉布迪威伊隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什麼問題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我之前提到過的織斑一夏的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊織斑教官的弟弟隊長也對其有好感的那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你先前告訴過我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的我的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情是這樣這次要去稱作臨海學校的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是關於要如何選擇泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全沒有頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望得到你那邊的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們黑兔子隊會始終與隊長同在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶問下隊長眼下所持有的裝備是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1件學校泳衣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得IS學園發的是舊式死庫水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個雖然也不算壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是僅憑那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是達不到出彩的境界的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是黑兔子隊的副隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒白看那些日本動漫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼我有奇策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是11點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到傍晚為止是自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在晚餐時間前必須回旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都記住了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個織斑和我們一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來打沙灘排球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯好啊在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦好高好高可以看到很遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呀你是貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊好像很好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來輪到我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是展望台給我適可而止點快下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了不就明白了移動監視塔遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏君你忘記在巴士里和我做的約定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧一夏就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是想要讓一夏幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見讓他幫我塗防曬霜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不遵守和女士的約定可不是紳士所為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請先用手加溫一下再塗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思因為這種事情是第一次做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次啊那還真是沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊為什麼看上去那麼高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇好像很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都心跳加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉亞等一下也把防曬霜借我用下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個只要背上塗就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不難得你幫我塗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己不方便塗到的地方都拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳和那個…臀部也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊我來幫你塗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈…好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個角落都幫你塗到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!? 這邊也想要塗吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我塗我塗我塗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴小姐你給我適可而止一點……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡為什麼是我挨揍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏我們比誰先到那個浮標吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你輸了就請我吃聖代哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀隨便決定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵太卑鄙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對塞西莉亞是挺過意不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回就讓給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能輸給塞西莉亞和勞拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳…抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…一夏的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵鈴不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一場大難呢鈴同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你回旅館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不等等我還要和一夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹月同學可以稍微幫我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我不要緊了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那麼精神的話應該是不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏原來你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個浴巾怪物是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給一夏看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是沒關係該由我決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那聲音…是勞拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:17:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得換了泳衣當然要給一夏看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等我也是需要心理準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就我一個人和一夏去海裡玩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想笑的話就笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼奇怪的啊對吧一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我覺得很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎我可…可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次有人那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不是說好了嗎來打沙灘排球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇和織斑對戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是三對三呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑君加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德諾阿小姐也好好打
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們看看被稱為7月的summer devil的我的實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛我…可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞拉怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可愛被說可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說還在害羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊那傢伙是追上去比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想還是讓她一個人靜一靜比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙灘排球啊好像很有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也一起打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯怎麼樣織斑老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑老師像模特一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師您來吧換我下去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯一起打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑老師才是你喜歡的類型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和看我們穿泳衣的樣子的反應完全不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊情敵真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連織斑老師都得計算在內
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯千冬姐的確是強勁的敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以大意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏你大概誤解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要發球了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊千冬…織斑老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去似乎很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有什麼擔心的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是束的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前兩天和我聯繫過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞拉的VT系統的事情似乎和她無關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是7月7日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會出現吧那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然已經準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高到犯規的性能喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}(High End)　(Over Spec)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟「小白」平起平坐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台機體的名字叫...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「紅椿」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.76,0:23:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄逸的裙子和兔耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太有視覺衝擊力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了這裡 IS的關鍵人物終於登場？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.94,0:23:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像給筱之之小姐帶了什麼禮物過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:23:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲 沒有驚訝的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.73,0:24:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了出人意料的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.77,0:24:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Thin·Red·Line)\N 下回 站立於境界線上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.76,0:24:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(265,250)\fs60}下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.76,0:24:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(640,480)\shad5\fs60}「站立於境界線上」
